title: Why clarity before action is the most important feature we ever built
excerpt: >-
  Most task managers let you create a task called 'Fix the thing.' KeilHQ
  doesn't. Here's why the Clarity Engine changes everything about how teams
  execute.
category: Product
author: Alex Rivera
publishedDate: 2026-05-20
